What do you mean?

01:13:57.212 --> 01:13:58.211
If you want to eat down here,"

01:13:58.252 --> 01:14:00.130
you'll have to teach them something new
every day,

01:14:00.171 --> 01:14:03.258
otherwise you'll go hungry...
and it makes sense... complete sense...

01:14:03.300 --> 01:14:05.423
knowledge is the one true source of wealth
is it not?!

01:14:05.459 --> 01:14:07.010
What kinds of things do they want to know?

01:14:07.429 --> 01:14:08.430
Pfff... anything will do!

01:14:08.472 --> 01:14:11.387
From the elementary laws of physics to
the behavioral patterns of winkles...

01:14:11.423 --> 01:14:13.974
even how to cook garden peas.
I taught them to write

01:14:14.014 --> 01:14:16.275
And to paint, especially huge canvasses..."

01:14:16.310 --> 01:14:19.564
and to harness light using mirrors
And transport water from one place to another

01:14:19.604 --> 01:14:21.773
Yes...
that's true, but how did you know all that?

01:14:21.940 --> 01:14:25.111
Because the man who invented all those
wonderful things is my grandfather!

01:14:25.153 --> 01:14:25.901
Arthur?!

01:14:25.943 --> 01:14:26.778
Grandpa!

01:14:26.820 --> 01:14:31.530
Oh my grandson
I'm so happy to see you again!"

01:14:31.573 --> 01:14:34.241
Let me look at you... my, how you've grown!

01:14:34.283 --> 01:14:35.496
It feels more like I've shrunk!

01:14:35.536 --> 01:14:38.455
Yes, that's true.
But how did you manage to get down here?

01:14:38.496 --> 01:14:40.082
Well, I found your riddle

01:14:40.124 --> 01:14:43.584
Oh, yes, of course! My riddle
oh, you are a true hero!

01:14:43.627 --> 01:14:45.797
Hello, Archibald, remember me?

01:14:45.839 --> 01:14:48.463
Betameche?! Is that really you?

01:14:48.505 --> 01:14:50.713
Oh... I'm so happy to see you again..."

01:14:50.755 --> 01:14:52.091
How is your father, that noble king?

01:14:52.133 --> 01:14:53.508
Very well indeed, thank you.

01:14:53.549 --> 01:14:57.097
and your sister, the charming Princess Selenia?

01:14:59.057 --> 01:15:00.391
Selenia!

01:15:00.891 --> 01:15:06.062
I failed, Arthur... I'm sorry, all is lost!

01:15:06.104 --> 01:15:07.814
No, as long as we're still alive"

01:15:07.856 --> 01:15:09.771
and love each other, nothing will ever be lost

01:15:09.813 --> 01:15:11.313
You are so full of hope!

01:15:11.438 --> 01:15:13.066
You can never give up hope."

01:15:13.108 --> 01:15:16.404
Look at me, only yesterday
I was just a small, lonely kid,

01:15:16.439 --> 01:15:19.032
and today, well, I married a princess!

01:15:19.073 --> 01:15:21.075
a happy princess.

01:15:21.575 --> 01:15:25.286
Because she's finally found her prince charming

01:15:28.580 --> 01:15:29.914
W- W-Whoa! Time out!

01:15:29.956 --> 01:15:30.917
I don't mean to be rude,"

01:15:30.958 --> 01:15:33.418
but don't you think you
should maybe respect the tradition...?

01:15:33.794 --> 01:15:36.924
Hey, yes, he's right, what was I thinking?

01:15:36.964 --> 01:15:40.341
Oh, hey, Archibald...! how are you?

01:15:40.384 --> 01:15:42.011
Well, actually... not bad at all, Selenia,"

01:15:42.053 --> 01:15:43.261
what a pleasure to see you again

01:15:43.303 --> 01:15:44.308
Likewise, likewise!

01:15:44.343 --> 01:15:46.179
Selenia, what's this tradition business?

01:15:46.220 --> 01:15:47.720
Once the first kiss has been exchanged,

01:15:47.764 --> 01:15:49.352
then you have to wait another thousand years,

01:15:49.388 --> 01:15:51.392
because then desire
and faith have to be put to the test...

01:15:51.433 --> 01:15:53.061
that which is rare is always valued highly

01:15:53.102 --> 01:15:54.230
She has a point, you know

01:15:54.312 --> 01:15:55.018
And as a Princess,"

01:15:55.061 --> 01:15:57.440
it is my duty to follow
the teachings of the Great Book...

01:15:57.482 --> 01:15:59.025
besides, you ought to do the same,

01:15:59.068 --> 01:16:00.401
instead of trying to steal kisses from me!

01:16:00.443 --> 01:16:02.901
Me? It wasn't me, you were the one

01:16:04.152 --> 01:16:08.240
Come along now, you two lovebirds
it's showtime!

01:16:09.739 --> 01:16:10.783
If you would care to

01:16:11.202 --> 01:16:13.330
Gate open, boss.

01:16:25.339 --> 01:16:26.379
My God...

01:16:26.421 --> 01:16:27.674
When I think that
it was I that taught them all this

01:16:27.716 --> 01:16:29.967
and now they are going to use it against us!

01:16:30.008 --> 01:16:32.135
And when I think
that I was the one who gave them the straws...!

01:16:44.770 --> 01:16:47.606
Look! It's Mino, Miro's son, he's still alive!

01:16:52.862 --> 01:16:54.114
the treasure!

01:16:58.744 --> 01:17:03.079
Ah, Archibald
what a great pleasure it is to see you again...

01:17:03.121 --> 01:17:04.253
The pleasure is all yours.

01:17:04.288 --> 01:17:05.080
So, Archibald
aren't you proud of the marvelous use"

01:17:05.122 --> 01:17:06.416
I've made of your knowledge?

01:17:06.457 --> 01:17:08.459
Looks like a fine structure...

01:17:08.501 --> 01:17:09.376
A shame it's only purpose...

01:17:09.416 --> 01:17:12.130
is to flood the Minimoys!

01:17:12.171 --> 01:17:13.462
Oh, no, not only that..."

01:17:13.506 --> 01:17:14.757
we are going to drown them,

01:17:14.797 --> 01:17:17.467
pulverize them, and destroy them forever.

01:17:17.510 --> 01:17:20.427
They will die in agony
with my name upon their lips

01:17:20.469 --> 01:17:22.930
Look... read my lips

01:17:22.973 --> 01:17:25.806
Mal-tha-zar

01:17:25.847 --> 01:17:27.183
You really are a monster!

01:17:27.225 --> 01:17:29.646
Maybe... but I also know how to be noble!

01:17:29.686 --> 01:17:31.228
You are free

01:17:35.690 --> 01:17:38.776
See?! All you have to do is follow this tunnel

01:17:38.816 --> 01:17:40.233
and you'll be home in no time!

01:17:40.274 --> 01:17:41.904
As soon as we're inside that tunnel
you'll flood it

01:17:41.945 --> 01:17:44.991
My poor Selenia
What a twisted mind you have! Come on

01:17:45.032 --> 01:17:46.907
hurry up, before I change my mind

01:17:46.948 --> 01:17:47.366
Sire?

01:17:47.408 --> 01:17:48.411
What is it now?

01:17:48.452 --> 01:17:51.747
May I ask You Highness to grant me
one last favor before I die

01:17:51.789 --> 01:17:53.624
I like this kid!

01:17:53.665 --> 01:17:54.543
what is this favor?

01:17:54.583 --> 01:17:56.374
I would like to leave my only valued possession,

01:17:56.410 --> 01:17:58.919
this bracelet, to my friend, Mino.

01:18:02.421 --> 01:18:03.339
Granted!

01:18:05.301 --> 01:18:07.009
Your father sent me! I'll get you out of here

01:18:07.050 --> 01:18:10.220
But you need to signal your
position at noon precisely!

01:18:10.429 --> 01:18:11.848
Signal my position, but how?

01:18:11.889 --> 01:18:13.893
Using your mirrors, Mino, mirrors...!

01:18:13.927 --> 01:18:15.222
Oh? Yes! Mmm... mirrors!

01:18:15.305 --> 01:18:16.141
That's enough!

01:18:16.184 --> 01:18:18.853
Patience is the only thing for which
I set myself a limit...!

01:18:18.894 --> 01:18:20.478
At noon... high noon, on the dot!

01:18:20.521 --> 01:18:23.730
I shall allow you a head start of... three minutes.

01:18:27.444 --> 01:18:29.235
I hope the burns in hell!

01:18:29.278 --> 01:18:31.280
He's already there, Selenia, hurry!

01:18:31.405 --> 01:18:32.405
Darkos?

01:18:32.449 --> 01:18:33.332
Yes, father?

01:18:33.367 --> 01:18:35.952
Prepare to open the floodgates

01:18:37.409 --> 01:18:39.329
Is there nothing to nibble?

01:18:40.829 --> 01:18:45.375
I do love something to nibble
on during a good show

01:18:46.419 --> 01:18:49.715
I can't go on...
and what's the point in running anyway?!

01:18:49.756 --> 01:18:51.131
Grandpa... come on, hurry

01:18:51.172 --> 01:18:53.173
You go on!
I'm staying here... to await my death...

01:18:53.216 --> 01:18:56.052
with a little dignity.

01:18:56.095 --> 01:18:57.844
Come on, Grandpa! You can do it

01:18:57.886 --> 01:19:00.096
Arthur! What's the point?
you must face up to it,

01:19:00.137 --> 01:19:01.682
son, we're done for.

01:19:03.892 --> 01:19:05.978
Your Highness, a few tasty tidbits

01:19:09.313 --> 01:19:13.608
Mmm, delicious! Bring me more!

01:19:13.858 --> 01:19:16.320
There must be a solution!
There's always a solution

01:19:16.402 --> 01:19:17.902
The only solution is to pray,"

01:19:17.937 --> 01:19:19.404
my children... pray for a miracle

01:19:19.438 --> 01:19:19.945
The problem is,"

01:19:19.987 --> 01:19:21.740
I've already asked the Great Goddess of
the Forest for so many miracles...

01:19:21.781 --> 01:19:23.448
I'm afraid she might get mad!

01:19:30.705 --> 01:19:31.454
A miracle!

01:19:31.497 --> 01:19:32.583
A miracle, where?!

01:19:32.626 --> 01:19:34.834
Right here, Grandpa, you're sitting on it.

01:19:34.877 --> 01:19:36.044
Look!

01:19:36.210 --> 01:19:37.753
Come and give me a hand...!

01:19:39.506 --> 01:19:41.090
Come on... push!

01:19:41.632 --> 01:19:44.178
Oh

01:19:45.011 --> 01:19:46.137
What is this thing?

01:19:46.219 --> 01:19:49.350
It's a car.
It's a Ferrari 250 GTI 12-cylinder...!

01:19:49.385 --> 01:19:50.231
It's a birthday present!

01:19:50.266 --> 01:19:51.637
Don't tell me you know how to drive that thing?

01:19:51.679 --> 01:19:52.766
Of course I do!

01:19:52.806 --> 01:19:53.977
If the young lady would care to step this way

01:19:54.019 --> 01:19:55.518
Oh God, whatever!

01:20:00.900 --> 01:20:01.940
Bingo!

01:20:19.041 --> 01:20:20.207
Hurry, Arthur, please get in!

01:20:20.249 --> 01:20:21.249
If we want make it the whole way,"

01:20:21.334 --> 01:20:22.628
we have to wind it up as far as it will go.

01:20:22.669 --> 01:20:23.753
Arthur, the water is coming!

01:20:23.795 --> 01:20:25.255
Hurry, Arthur, please.

01:20:25.289 --> 01:20:25.922
Got it!

01:20:25.963 --> 01:20:28.130
this is the first time I've ever taken
a girl out for a drive, you know!

01:20:28.172 --> 01:20:30.298
Well, let's just hope it won't
be the last... Step on it!

01:20:30.506 --> 01:20:32.341
We're off!

01:20:34.471 --> 01:20:36.345
Faster!

01:20:41.186 --> 01:20:42.435
I just hope there aren't any speed
cameras down here,

01:20:42.476 --> 01:20:43.561
or we've had it!

01:20:43.602 --> 01:20:45.064
Hey, go to the left!

01:20:48.605 --> 01:20:51.778
I'd appreciate a little more warning
next time if that's OK with you?

01:20:51.820 --> 01:20:53.401
OK, Turn right.

01:20:55.738 --> 01:20:57.198
Which way do I go now, left or right?

01:20:57.239 --> 01:20:58.490
Down!

01:21:02.036 --> 01:21:03.455
Selenia... I... I don't feel so good!

01:21:03.497 --> 01:21:06.369
Just hang in there, the road is smoother now.

01:21:15.673 --> 01:21:16.378
Arthur

01:21:16.420 --> 01:21:18.216
Honey, do you hear that strange noise?"

01:21:18.258 --> 01:21:19.509
It sounds like
there's running water underneath.

01:21:19.551 --> 01:21:23.054
Oh great, now you're hearing voice
just like Joan of Arc did?"

01:21:23.095 --> 01:21:24.886
Next thing you know you're gonna
be seeing little angels

01:21:24.929 --> 01:21:29.307
and great big ghosts
with spears and armor coming after you

01:21:29.349 --> 01:21:31.142
Wait wait, you might want to turn around,"

01:21:31.186 --> 01:21:34.396
there's, there's large men
with necklaces and feathers

01:21:35.230 --> 01:21:36.607
and I don't know... I...

01:21:37.442 --> 01:21:38.986
What the...

01:21:43.653 --> 01:21:44.487
What time is it?

01:21:44.528 --> 01:21:46.572
The time?! sure!

01:21:46.615 --> 01:21:48.072
According to our calculations,"

01:21:48.114 --> 01:21:50.952
the water should hit
the village in three balls time.

01:21:51.870 --> 01:21:53.374
What time is it, my dear Miro?

01:21:53.415 --> 01:21:54.999
Five to noon, my good king.

01:21:55.040 --> 01:21:57.207
Only five minutes left and still...
no news.

01:21:57.250 --> 01:21:58.165
Have faith in them, my good king..."

01:21:58.207 --> 01:21:59.585
I am sure that they will succeed.

01:21:59.627 --> 01:22:02.959
May the Gods hear you
Miro, may the gods hear you...

01:22:13.013 --> 01:22:14.847
Look, there's the gate!

01:22:14.887 --> 01:22:15.600
Yes

01:22:15.808 --> 01:22:18.517
We made it!

01:22:19.101 --> 01:22:24.188
Arthur
you're not going break down on us now?!

01:22:24.231 --> 01:22:26.733
Sorry
I guess we're gonna have to get out and... RUN!

01:22:30.528 --> 01:22:32.195
What is that rumbling noise?

01:22:32.279 --> 01:22:34.948
I have no idea, Sire
but I have a terrible foreboding

01:22:35.447 --> 01:22:37.785
Father, it's me, Selenia!

01:22:37.826 --> 01:22:39.369
My daughter... they have returned!

01:22:39.410 --> 01:22:42.037
Open the gate!

01:22:42.078 --> 01:22:44.121
Open the gate now!

01:22:50.337 --> 01:22:51.464
Close the gate immediately!

01:22:51.506 --> 01:22:53.425
Open it, close it, make up your mind

01:22:53.466 --> 01:22:55.591
All together now!

01:23:06.601 --> 01:23:08.317
You did it daddy, you did it!"

01:23:08.352 --> 01:23:11.688
You are now the uncontested Master
of all the Kingdoms!

01:23:11.730 --> 01:23:12.730
Heaven knows,"

01:23:12.773 --> 01:23:15.151
I don't care about titles and honors,

01:23:15.193 --> 01:23:18.735
but I must admit that it does feel good
to be Supreme Ruler.

01:23:18.777 --> 01:23:20.404
Let us prepare ourselves.

01:23:23.406 --> 01:23:24.991
The gate looks as if it will hold.

01:23:25.033 --> 01:23:25.825
Not for long!

01:23:25.866 --> 01:23:26.368
It will!

01:23:26.410 --> 01:23:27.659
Oh, my children!

01:23:27.699 --> 01:23:27.950
Papa!

01:23:27.991 --> 01:23:29.079
Daddy!

01:23:30.121 --> 01:23:31.457
We missed you, Papa

01:23:31.497 --> 01:23:32.289
Oh, my children,"

01:23:32.332 --> 01:23:34.626
Oh, my children, you're this old king's
most prized possessions.

01:23:56.058 --> 01:23:57.059
What's wrong?

01:23:58.690 --> 01:24:01.564
No, the phone's cut off, it doesn't work.

01:24:01.606 --> 01:24:02.981
What is wrong?!

01:24:03.483 --> 01:24:05.070
AHHHH... Ou... out there!

01:24:05.112 --> 01:24:06.068
What's out there?

01:24:06.111 --> 01:24:06.737
Five!

01:24:06.778 --> 01:24:07.610
Five what?

01:24:07.651 --> 01:24:08.990
Blllllaaaaaack!

01:24:09.031 --> 01:24:10.658
What are you talking about?

01:24:10.700 --> 01:24:11.698
Huge!
(panicky whispers, then, LOUD)

01:24:11.823 --> 01:24:12.656
Where're you going?"

01:24:12.699 --> 01:24:14.825
Don't leave me here,
no Granny please!

01:24:17.785 --> 01:24:20.123
it's noon!

01:24:20.915 --> 01:24:22.417
In one minute!

01:24:23.499 --> 01:24:26.004
Hurry now, you only have one minute.

01:24:26.045 --> 01:24:28.200
We can only hold the water back
for about an hour,

01:24:28.300 --> 01:24:29.591
but I know that I can
depend on you.

01:24:30.133 --> 01:24:31.509
After all, you're one of us now,

01:24:31.550 --> 01:24:34.450
and I hope you know that
you're always welcome back here.

01:24:35.300 --> 01:24:38.000
And a second turn of
the wheel for the spirit.

01:24:38.905 --> 01:24:40.500
Our lives are in your hands, my friend.

01:24:40.800 --> 01:24:42.521
We're counting on you
and your grandson.

01:24:42.567 --> 01:24:45.228
Don't worry. Arthur has a plan,
and I'm sure it's gonna work.

01:24:48.599 --> 01:24:50.109
It's gonna be pretty dull
around here without you.

01:24:50.191 --> 01:24:50.942
Come back soon, huh?

01:24:50.984 --> 01:24:53.815
At the tenth moon, that's promise.

01:24:57.863 --> 01:25:00.491
Ten moons, that gives us plenty
of time to put our desire

01:25:00.533 --> 01:25:03.117
to the test and respect the protocol!

01:25:03.160 --> 01:25:05.954
To hell with the protocol!

01:25:07.831 --> 01:25:10.500
and a third turn of the wheel for the soul.

01:25:28.099 --> 01:25:31.722
See you... ten moons!

01:25:37.851 --> 01:25:42.850
Thank you! You okay? Yeah, thanks!

01:25:42.891 --> 01:25:44.059
Mom?

01:25:44.101 --> 01:25:45.972
Mom...! Mom?

01:25:46.014 --> 01:25:48.931
Honey, what, get out... what...

01:25:51.717 --> 01:25:55.342
oh! Arthur! where have you been?

01:25:55.382 --> 01:25:56.256
I was with the Minimoys

01:25:56.298 --> 01:25:57.634
The Min... Miniwhat?

01:25:57.675 --> 01:25:59.007
The Minimoys!

01:25:59.049 --> 01:26:02.877
Oooh... Ha, ha!

01:26:02.919 --> 01:26:04.297
Mom?!

01:26:04.338 --> 01:26:05.585
Oh Granpa!

01:26:06.462 --> 01:26:07.960
Are you okay?

01:26:08.001 --> 01:26:11.457
My brothers!
Oh I'm so glad to see you again!

01:26:11.498 --> 01:26:17.414
Grandpa! We've got no time left
we gotta go!

01:26:17.455 --> 01:26:19.288
You're right

01:26:20.786 --> 01:26:23.116
Noon on the dot!

01:26:23.158 --> 01:26:25.156
and no one in sight!

01:26:25.197 --> 01:26:27.616
I'm afraid
though it is a beautiful Sunday

01:26:27.657 --> 01:26:29.320
despite it being the day of our Lord...

01:26:29.365 --> 01:26:32.904
there seems to be no miracle! So

01:26:34.238 --> 01:26:36.985
You're right Davido

01:26:37.028 --> 01:26:38.566
it is a beautiful, beautiful Sunday!

01:26:38.600 --> 01:26:40.106
I believe we have some papers to sign

01:26:40.149 --> 01:26:41.151
am I right?

01:26:41.193 --> 01:26:42.106
Let's go in the living room,

01:26:42.149 --> 01:26:43.606
we'll be more comfortable!

01:26:48.977 --> 01:26:50.224
While I try to buy time,

01:26:50.266 --> 01:26:51.145
you get busy finding the treasure

01:26:51.188 --> 01:26:52.308
OK!

01:27:00.013 --> 01:27:05.300
Mino, Mino where are you? Mino!

01:27:05.341 --> 01:27:07.925
This is not gonna be easy!

01:27:12.590 --> 01:27:14.046
Light!

01:27:36.533 --> 01:27:39.197
I promised you riches and power

01:27:39.241 --> 01:27:42.157
And Malthazar always keeps his promises.

01:27:42.199 --> 01:27:44.155
nothing can stop us now!

01:27:44.197 --> 01:27:47.195
The Seven Kingdoms are... mine!

01:27:49.068 --> 01:27:50.900
I mean, of course, ours

01:27:54.816 --> 01:27:56.190
What?

01:27:56.232 --> 01:27:57.358
Excuse me,

01:27:57.397 --> 01:27:58.483
could you tell me what time it is,

01:27:58.522 --> 01:28:00.230
I'm kinda far-sighted

01:28:01.270 --> 01:28:02.896
NOON!

01:28:02.939 --> 01:28:03.976
Thank you!

01:28:04.017 --> 01:28:06.308
My fearless and faithful warriors!

01:28:06.350 --> 01:28:08.975
...let the festivities begin.

01:28:13.472 --> 01:28:15.095
Now if I do the exact opposite,

01:28:15.135 --> 01:28:18.051
the light which reflects downwards should
then reflect... upwards!

01:28:26.252 --> 01:28:28.380
Mino! You're the best.

01:28:30.709 --> 01:28:32.551
But what is he doing? Darkos!?

01:28:32.585 --> 01:28:34.251
That idiot will give our position away!

01:28:34.293 --> 01:28:35.873
Make him cut that beam immediately!

01:28:36.375 --> 01:28:37.748
Cut the beam!

01:28:37.790 --> 01:28:39.791
Huh? Uh, sorry, because I'm far sighted,

01:28:39.832 --> 01:28:40.756
but I'm also hard of hearing!

01:28:40.792 --> 01:28:45.829
You fool! You will be sorry
that you defied Malthazar!

01:28:51.241 --> 01:28:52.365
Oh, it's nothing, really!

01:28:52.575 --> 01:28:53.783
Bring him here!

01:28:53.825 --> 01:28:56.216
Watch out! I can get really nasty!

01:28:56.251 --> 01:28:58.614
Sure you can... come on, show us!

01:29:15.185 --> 01:29:16.726
WHAT IS THIS THING?

01:29:16.768 --> 01:29:20.805
I know, I know... Oh gracious Lord
it's a kind of

01:29:41.628 --> 01:29:42.710
Damn!

01:29:42.752 --> 01:29:48.251
Father! What shall I do?
What about me, father?

01:29:53.667 --> 01:29:56.789
As for you, my son...

01:29:56.831 --> 01:30:00.368
I hereby solemnly appoint you Commander
of the Imperial Forces!

01:30:00.741 --> 01:30:02.332
Oh... thank you, father, that's nice

01:30:02.367 --> 01:30:03.911
but... you wouldn't have a place left
on that mosquito of yours,

01:30:03.993 --> 01:30:04.740
would you?!

01:30:04.782 --> 01:30:07.157
A Commander never deserts his post...!

01:30:09.699 --> 01:30:13.276
Father... Daddy!?

01:30:18.024 --> 01:30:25.937
Mino? Yes!

01:30:30.603 --> 01:30:32.225
More coffee?

01:30:32.269 --> 01:30:34.391
No! No more coffee! Thank you!

01:30:34.433 --> 01:30:36.681
But what I would love is
for you to sign the paper!

01:30:36.722 --> 01:30:39.221
Of course, what did I do with my pen?

01:30:41.596 --> 01:30:43.093
Oh what a lovely pen!

01:30:43.135 --> 01:30:44.551
We have wasted enough time.

01:30:44.594 --> 01:30:45.557
Sign!

01:30:45.592 --> 01:30:46.676
Of course.

01:30:52.424 --> 01:30:56.338
And now... the money!

01:30:56.379 --> 01:31:00.128
Hm? Oh the money, yes!

01:31:00.169 --> 01:31:02.251
I'd like to see how you're going to
pull one of your tricks now!

01:31:02.285 --> 01:31:03.622
Here!

01:31:05.665 --> 01:31:07.331
Bravo my boy!

01:31:12.996 --> 01:31:19.948
So then... good accounts make
for good friends isn't that right?

01:31:20.407 --> 01:31:23.696
There you are, paid in full!

01:31:29.068 --> 01:31:32.110
Sir, I must now be saying goodbye!

01:31:32.150 --> 01:31:33.275
Good bye now.

01:31:33.316 --> 01:31:35.397
Good bye!

01:31:45.019 --> 01:31:46.297
Congratulations!

01:31:47.328 --> 01:31:48.441
Nobody move!

01:31:48.482 --> 01:31:50.215
I said!

01:31:56.772 --> 01:31:59.368
So that's why you
had your sights set on this land?

01:31:59.410 --> 01:32:02.589
Of course! The call of greed
now and forever!

01:32:02.621 --> 01:32:03.952
One night you had a few too many,

01:32:03.992 --> 01:32:05.560
and you told me about this treasure,

01:32:05.603 --> 01:32:07.872
and ever since
I have not had a good night's sleep!

01:32:07.913 --> 01:32:09.767
But now, it's mine!

01:32:09.807 --> 01:32:12.158
Thanks kid! Nice job!

01:32:12.200 --> 01:32:13.932
Well, I'll be saying my farewells,

01:32:13.969 --> 01:32:15.668
you won't be seeing me ever again!

01:32:15.708 --> 01:32:19.911
Because, I am going far, far away!

01:32:21.068 --> 01:32:23.749
You're coming with me! Com'on!

01:32:24.245 --> 01:32:26.678
Get your hands off me.
I know the governor!

01:32:31.186 --> 01:32:32.860
I'll take that. I'll take that.

01:32:32.902 --> 01:32:35.205
Next time,
please, put your gift in a safer place.

01:32:35.247 --> 01:32:35.960
That's a promise.

01:32:36.002 --> 01:32:39.265
I'll take it.
It's much safer with me.

01:33:01.157 --> 01:33:02.623
Don't worry Mino,

01:33:02.665 --> 01:33:04.383
I'm gonna care of you.

01:33:12.753 --> 01:33:14.383
They did it!

01:33:14.802 --> 01:33:19.100
Yes, he made it, made it!
My son!

01:33:20.900 --> 01:33:23.000
Oh, my boy...

01:33:25.600 --> 01:33:29.035
Howl would have loved
my little Mino to see this!

01:33:29.078 --> 01:33:30.663
I understand Miro,

01:33:30.706 --> 01:33:32.463
but our people are safe and sound...

01:33:32.548 --> 01:33:34.599
and that is something to be
thankful for.

01:33:34.642 --> 01:33:36.189
Of course. of course.

01:33:43.770 --> 01:33:46.817
Wait, I think I know what it is

01:33:49.249 --> 01:33:50.797
Hey, it's Mino!

01:33:50.923 --> 01:33:52.638
Mino, my son!

01:33:52.783 --> 01:33:57.000
- Papa!
- Oh, my boy...

01:33:58.458 --> 01:33:59.294
Well, there you go!

01:33:59.633 --> 01:34:01.180
All's well that ends well!

01:34:01.271 --> 01:34:02.266
Not quite...

01:34:05.154 --> 01:34:05.781
May I?

01:34:42.490 --> 01:34:45.213
I think it's ready... Excuse me...

01:34:45.253 --> 01:34:48.015
Waited so long for this moment.

01:34:52.914 --> 01:34:55.130
I propose a toast!

01:34:55.172 --> 01:34:57.142
Here, here!

01:34:57.183 --> 01:34:58.647
Here it comes!

01:34:59.778 --> 01:35:01.949
What's that?

01:35:01.992 --> 01:35:03.127
My favorite dish!

01:35:03.169 --> 01:35:05.093
African giraffe's neck!

01:35:05.137 --> 01:35:06.097
What?

01:35:10.035 --> 01:35:13.085
Honey! Honey! Rosie!

01:35:13.125 --> 01:35:14.344
Wake up, honey!

01:35:15.513 --> 01:35:18.278
Every time she gets a little excited
over she goes!

01:35:21.079 --> 01:35:22.586
Where's Arthur?

01:35:23.384 --> 01:35:25.520
He, he just went to wash up.

01:35:25.559 --> 01:35:26.815
He'll be back in a jiffy!

01:35:42.177 --> 01:35:45.317
only ten more moons, Selenia

01:36:00.718 --> 01:36:02.016
I will wait for you.

